    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>All in the Neighborhood: Best Buy Eyes Yonkers Site</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Elsa Brenner</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Brenner, Elsa</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Best Buy Co threatens confrontation with P C Richard &amp; Son, The Wiz and Circuit City over plans to build store in Yonkers, NY (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Best Buy Company -- the nation's largest electronics retailer -- is considering a site in Yonkers that could pave the way for a four-way confrontation between other national chains that sell televisions, stereos and camcorders.</p>
        <p>If it moves to Yonkers, Best Buy would be only three stores away from P. C. Richard &amp; Son at the Bradlees Shopping Center, a quarter mile south of The Wiz and three miles north of Circuit City, in The Mall at Cross County, also in Yonkers.</p>
        <p>Elsa Brenner</p>
      </block>
